        {
          "datasource": { "type": "marcusolsson-json-datasource", "uid": "${json_datasource}" },
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "description": "List of archived benchmark runs. Use the Replay Manager API to load/unload runs:\n\n- Load: POST /runs/{id}/load\n- Unload: DELETE /runs/{id}/load\n- Delete: DELETE /runs/{id}"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Quick Reference\n\n| Action | Command |\n|---|---|\n| Export current run | `curl -X POST http://REPLAY_MANAGER:8080/runs -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"start\":\"...\",\"end\":\"...\"}'` |\n| Load a run | `curl -X POST http://REPLAY_MANAGER:8080/runs/<run_id>/load` |\n| Unload a run | `curl -X DELETE http://REPLAY_MANAGER:8080/runs/<run_id>/load` |\n| Delete a run | `curl -X DELETE http://REPLAY_MANAGER:8080/runs/<run_id>` |",
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false }
      },
      "title": "API Reference",
      "type": "text"
    }
